  fiber: 4 g
  sodium: 1290 mg
course: main course
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/brown-sugar-bacon-stuffed-french-toast-64ad64e208c61453c499a9c6
cuisine: North America
